          "rawSql": "-- Sample Time Series Query\n-- Replace 'your_schema.your_table' with your actual table\n-- Replace 'timestamp_column' and 'value_column' with your columns\n\nSELECT \n    timestamp_column AS time,\n    value_column AS value\nFROM your_schema.your_table\nWHERE $__timeFilter(timestamp_column)\nORDER BY timestamp_column",
